#

Spiced Lentil & Vegetable Stew

$15.99
350 kcal

Dietary Tags:

VeganHigh ProteinGluten Free

Tags:

HeartyComfort FoodVegetarian

Description

A hearty and flavorful stew packed with lentils, seasonal vegetables, and aromatic spices, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • Green lentils: 1 cup
  • Carrots: 2, diced
  • Celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • Onion: 1, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • Cumin seeds: 1 tsp
  • Turmeric powder: 1 tsp
  • Coriander powder: 1 tsp
  • Vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • Spinach: 2 cups, fresh
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
